Ex3:Apply boarder to an image with css 
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Sample List style</title>
    <style>
        .borderstyle {
            padding: 25px;
            border: 6px solid forestgreen;
        }

        .colorborder {
            border-style: dotted;
            border-color: blueviolet;
            padding: 30px;
        }

        .imageborder {
            border: 1px solid red;
            padding: 5px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="borderstyle">
        <p>Some content will be there in p tag and we will apply border with CSS to the </p>
    </div>

    <div class="colorborder">
        <p>Some content will be there in p tag and we will apply border with CSS to the </p>
    </div>

    <div class="imageborder">
        <img src="/img/flower" alt="flower">
    </div>
</body>
</html>
